      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 57 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 57 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：進退，利武人之貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject (now) advancing, (now) receding. It would be advantageous for him to have the firm correctness of a brave soldier.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
