      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 57 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 57 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：頻巽，吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows its subject penetrating (only) by violent and repeated efforts. There will be occasion for regret.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
