      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 57 六四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 57 六四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：悔亡，田獲三品。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows all occasion for repentance (in its subject) passed away. He takes game for its threefold use in his hunting.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
